{"tid":510363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲沉迷是種病症？ 世衛組織明年將編撰列入《國際疾病分類》","createTime":"2017-12-26T11:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T12:46:44.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1422520c20d67e416da8441acdaa96fe426078","tid":510363,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"遊戲沉迷是種病症？ 世衛組織明年將編撰列入《國際疾病分類》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2291775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2291775&d=ZmHNpoj58Zsne7T%2F4trR1BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=aeacd176\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2291775&h=9b03f02b\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2291775</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者陳耀宗／外電報導〕打太多遊戲也會被視為一種疾病嗎？根據外媒報導，世界衛生組織（WHO）很快就會在明年點頭認同，自1990年後就沒有被修正過的《國際疾病分類》將在明年進行改版，最新版本「ICD-11」將會把「遊戲失調」（Gaming Disorder）納入。<br />\n<br />\n《國際疾病分類》（International Classification of Diseases）是由世界衛生組織（WHO）所編撰，該著作被廣泛為各國醫界作為臨床診斷參考的指南。<br />\n<br />\n根據《New Scientist》報導，遊戲失調在「ICD-11」中的內容還尚未完成，但以目前草稿來看，將是供臨床醫生診斷、確認一位民眾的遊玩遊戲程度是否成為一項嚴重的健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n根據這份草稿，如果有人得到「遊戲失調」症狀，就代表他們將「玩遊戲優先於其他生活中的利益，就算會導致負面影響，依舊想法不減，且持續超過一年」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/194034_19b223de78e24b4d538df7a3c6ac47de.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F194034_19b223de78e24b4d538df7a3c6ac47de.jpeg&h=1aca808e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7369d5bed14efed32fcbc4393db645aa903a6c07","tid":510363,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"係都加左沉迷打飛機同睇av先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdca22fe7ad0d249800546f5f9597e38636c5334","tid":510363,"uid":162073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"窮己經係病啦,正一on9"},{"pid":"264b472e0ffe4ec5254b75c1e677e8b27f63581d","tid":510363,"uid":91783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"世衛有富奸Fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5170ab1bb6ed7bef5985efb3b3047c7cdec40af","tid":510363,"uid":51129,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"有冇沉迷返工病？<br />\n症狀：「返工優先於其他生活中的利益，就算會導致負面影響，依舊想法不減，且持續超過一年」"},{"pid":"bc76cef0306973be2be2252d44a4dc3d2da29a09","tid":510363,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"打機上癮好易治療<br />\n<br />\n畀啲benzo班打機高手食  食到佢懵下懵下<br />\n<br />\n表現大不如前  自然對打機失去信心 從而戒除打機癮"},{"pid":"61c33d7834c11fb6f74d455c634e12978dd34175","tid":510363,"uid":62506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"世衛養埋成班人食飽飯無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3593a81c0cd2dbc352a83e5be13500ec0aad8f","tid":510363,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"貪污系米病<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逃稅系米病<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bed4195e21f10a27d3ec5f9580d8b08ab3ff33","tid":510363,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61c33d7834c11fb6f74d455c634e12978dd34175","tid":510363,"uid":62506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"世衛養埋成班人食飽飯無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"成班撚頭啲思維仲停係80年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6903f32396ddf378afb03721bbc0a4c4ea5b8219","tid":510363,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"遊戲病 ex-aid呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo